    • Class de.charite.compbio.jannovar.reference.TranscriptModel extends Object implements Serializable

      serialVersionUID:
      3L

      • Serialized Fields

        • accession

          String accession
          Accession number of the transcript (e.g., the UCSC knownGene id - uc011nca.2). The version number may be included.

        • geneSymbol

          String geneSymbol
          Gene symbol of the known Gene. Can be null for some genes. Note that in annovar, $name2 corresponds to the geneSymbol if available, otherwise the kgID is used.

        • txRegion

          GenomeInterval txRegion
          Genomic interval with transcript begin/end.

        • cdsRegion

          GenomeInterval cdsRegion
          Genomic interval with CDS begin/end. Note that in Jannovar, the CDS region includes the start and stop codon.

        • exonRegions

          com.google.common.collect.ImmutableList<E> exonRegions
          Genomic intervals with the exons, order is dictated by strand of transcript.

        • sequence

          String sequence
          cDNA sequence of the spliced RNA of this known gene transcript.

        • geneID

          String geneID
          The gene ID, from Ensembl ("ENS[MUS]*G0+([0-9]+)"), Entrez ("ENTREZ([0-9]+) "), RefSeq ("gene([0-9]+)"). null for no available gene ID.

        • transcriptSupportLevel

          int transcriptSupportLevel
          The transcript support level of the this transcript (the lower the better).
          See Also:
          TranscriptSupportLevels, http://www.ensembl.org/Help/Glossary?id=492
